query:
INSERT INTO
                via_withdrawals (id, l2_tx_hash, l2_tx_log_index, receiver, value)
                VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
                ON CONFLICT (id)
                DO UPDATE SET
                value = excluded.value,
                l2_tx_hash = CASE
                    WHEN excluded.l2_tx_hash <> '' THEN excluded.l2_tx_hash
                    ELSE via_withdrawals.l2_tx_hash
                END,
                updated_at = NOW();
